A 35-year-old man Abel Mavasa from Xitlalani Village outside
Malamulele has accused a construction company and the Collins Chabane
Municipality of failing him.Mavasa says Ndhuna Construction didn't properly do their job
- after he crashed into a storm drainage system.According to the complainant, the incident occurred in
